OL,3,CBoy, 11, injured after children find
OL,4,Cgun in woodland near Southampton
OL,6,FAn 11-year-old boy has been injured
OL,7,Fafter discovering a gun in woodland
OL,8,Fnear Southampton.
OL,10,FPolice say two boys found what they
OL,11,Fthought was a BB gun in woods close to
OL,12,FTickleford Drive in Weston, and took
OL,13,Fit back to their house.
OL,15,FThe firearm was accidentally
OL,16,Fdischarged and a boy aged 11 was
OL,17,Ftreated for a graze to his head.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/5
