OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1775837470
OL,3,CBoy, 11, injured after children find
OL,4,Cgun in woodland near Southampton
OL,6,FHampshire Police have launched an
OL,7,Finvestigation and say searches of the
OL,8,Farea where the gun was found have been
OL,9,Fcarried out.
OL,11,FA scene watch remains in place.
OL,13,FChief Inspector Chris Douglas, deputy
OL,14,Fdistrict commander for Southampton,
OL,15,Fsaid: "As soon as this incident was
OL,16,Freported to us on Tuesday, our teams
OL,17,Fwere swiftly in attendance and have
OL,18,Fbeen carrying out thorough enquiries
OL,19,Fand searches in the area since.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/5
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,420,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1775837470
OL,3,CBoy, 11, injured after children find
OL,4,Cgun in woodland near Southampton
OL,6,F"We know that our scenes will have
OL,7,Fdisrupted people's normal daily
OL,8,Froutines, and we want to thank local
OL,9,Fresidents for their patience as we
OL,10,Fcarry out our investigation.
OL,12,F"Thankfully, this discovery has not
OL,13,Fresulted in more serious injuries, and
OL,14,Fthe boys and their families have acted
OL,15,Fquickly to report the matter to us and
OL,16,Fallow us start further enquiries.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/5
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,420,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1775837470
OL,3,CBoy, 11, injured after children find
OL,4,Cgun in woodland near Southampton
OL,6,F"These kinds of firearms are often
OL,7,Fused to threaten people, and cause
OL,8,Fserious harm, and we are committed to
OL,9,Ftackling and disrupting serious
OL,10,Fcriminal activity.
OL,12,F"Our teams remain in the area today,
OL,13,Fand will be conducting patrols and
OL,14,Fhouse to house enquiries, if you do
OL,15,Fhave any concerns or questions, then
OL,16,Fplease do not hesitate to speak with
OL,17,Fthem."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/5
